Frequently Asked Questions
What is the Bolay's address?
Bolay is located at 2905 SW 42nd St, Gainesville, FL 32608, USA. This is where you will go to get DoorDash Pickup orders, and where Dashers will go to get your DoorDash delivery orders.
Does Bolay offer delivery or pickup?
You can browse Bolay’s menu and place an order for both Delivery and Pickup on DoorDash. Bolay may also offer delivery and pickup on their own or through other delivery services.
What is Bolay's rating?
Bolay is rated 4.8/5 stars by DoorDash users.
What are the most popular dishes at Bolay?
The dishes most commonly ordered by DoorDash customers at Bolay are Regular Bol, Large Bol and Strawberry Chia Seed Pudding .
Is Bolay a DashPass eligible store?
Bolay offers DashPass benefits like $0 delivery, reduced service fees, and $5 credits back on Pickup orders. If you want to know if a store is DashPass eligible, you can look for the DashPass icon next to their name.
